OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPM pledges trans guidance  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor schools 'for summer'   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rishi Sunak has promised schools will  
OL,6, receive guidance on policies for       
OL,7, transgender pupils for the summer term.
OL,9,FThe Prime Minister intervened after a  
OL,10,Fteaching union said its members were   
OL,11,Fnavigating a 'minefield' around gender.
OL,13,FHe was asked about a report from a     
OL,14,Fcentre-right think tank Policy Exchange
OL,15,Fwhich looked at 154 English secondary  
OL,16,Fschools.                               
OL,18,FIt found only 39 of them reliably      
OL,19,Finformed parents when pupils identified
OL,20,Fas trans or questioned their gender,   
